[normal]The rail industry produced a set of scenarios a few years ago that illustrate the process well, and it would be valuable to carry out such scenario planning for autonomous road vehicles and 
[normal]intelligent transport infrastructure. It is certainly essential for relevant scenarios to be explored before the technologies mature. 
